Machine Learning Model for House Pricing Prediction

Description: Developed a regression model to predict house prices using a dataset of various features.

Technologies Used: Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib.

Key Contributions:

Performed Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) to identify key features affecting house prices.

Cleaned and preprocessed raw data, handling missing values and categorical variables.

Implemented and trained a linear regression model (or other appropriate models) to predict house prices.

Evaluated model performance using metrics such as Mean Squared Error (MSE) and R-squared.

Visualized model results to demonstrate performance and insights.
